education: Most of these occupations require a four-year bachelor's degree, but some do not.
job_training: Employees in these occupations usually need several years of work-related experience, on-the-job training, and/or vocational training.

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to concentrate on a task over a period of time without being distracted.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Study a technical manual while listening to loud construction sounds
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Answer a business call with coworkers talking nearby

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to shift back and forth between two or more activities or sources of information (such as speech, sounds, touch, or other sources).
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Monitor radar and radio transmissions to keep track of heavy aircraft traffic
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Listen to music while entering numbers into a spreadsheet

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to generate or use different sets of rules for combining or grouping things in different ways.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Classify man-made fibers in terms of their characteristics, like strength or cost
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Sort paintbrushes based on length

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to apply general rules to specific problems to produce answers that make sense.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Design an aircraft wing using principles of aerodynamics
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Know that a stalled car can coast downhill

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to come up with a number of ideas about a topic (the number of ideas is important, not their quality, correctness, or creativity).
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Identify as many strategies as possible for a company acquisition and merger
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Name four different uses for a screwdriver

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to combine pieces of information to form general rules or conclusions (includes finding a relationship among seemingly unrelated events).
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Diagnose a disease using results of many different lab tests
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Decide what to wear based on the weather report

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to arrange things or actions in a certain order or pattern according to a specific rule or set of rules (e.g., patterns of numbers, letters, words, pictures, mathematical operations).
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Assemble a wind turbine
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Put things in numerical order

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to come up with unusual or clever ideas about a given topic or situation, or to develop creative ways to solve a problem.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Invent a new type of man-made fiber
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Use a credit card to open a locked door

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to tell when something is wrong or is likely to go wrong. It does not involve solving the problem, only recognizing there is a problem.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Recognize an illness at an early stage of a disease when there are only a few symptoms
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Recognize that an unplugged lamp won't work

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to remember information such as words, numbers, pictures, and procedures.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Recite a 300-word speech after studying it for 15 minutes
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Remember the number on your bus to be sure you get back on the right one

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to identify or detect a known pattern (a figure, object, word, or sound) that is hidden in other distracting material.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Identify camouflaged animals from a moving vehicle while on a safari
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Detect that your phone is ringing while at a concert

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to quickly and accurately compare similarities and differences among sets of letters, numbers, objects, pictures, or patterns. The things to be compared may be presented at the same time or one after the other. This ability also includes comparing a presented object with a remembered object.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Inspect electrical parts for defects as they pass on a fast-moving assembly line
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Sort mail according to ZIP codes with no time pressure

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to quickly make sense of, combine, and organize information into meaningful patterns.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Interpret patterns on weather radar to decide if the weather is changing
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Recognize a song after hearing only the first few notes

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to choose the right mathematical methods or formulas to solve a problem.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Determine the mathematics required to simulate a space craft landing on the moon
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Determine how much 20 oranges will cost when they are priced at 5 for 4 dollars

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to add, subtract, multiply, or divide quickly and correctly.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Compute the interest payment that should be generated from an investment
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Add 2 and 7

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to know your location in relation to the environment or to know where other objects are in relation to you.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Navigate an ocean voyage using a compass and landmarks
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Use the floor plan to locate a store in a mall

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to imagine how something will look after it is moved around or when its parts are moved or rearranged.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Anticipate future moves in a chess game
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Imagine how to place paper in a printer so that the letterhead comes out on top

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to listen to and understand information and ideas presented through spoken words and sentences.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Understand a lecture on advanced physics
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Understand a television commercial

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to communicate information and ideas in speaking so others will understand.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Explain advanced principles of genetics to college freshmen
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Place an order at a restaurant drive-thru

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to read and understand information and ideas presented in writing.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Understand an instruction book on repairing Artificial Intelligence systems
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Understand signs on the highway

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to communicate information and ideas in writing so others will understand.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Write an advanced economics textbook
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Write a note to remind someone to take food out of the freezer

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to exert yourself physically over long periods of time without getting winded or out of breath.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Run 10 miles
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Walk 1/4 mile

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to quickly and repeatedly bend, stretch, twist, or reach out with your body, arms, and/or legs.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Maneuver a kayak through swift rapids
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Hand pick a bushel of apples from a tree

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to bend, stretch, twist, or reach with your body, arms, and/or legs.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Work under the dashboard of a car
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Reach to adjust the radio in a car

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to coordinate the movement of your arms, legs, and torso together when the whole body is in motion.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Perform a ballet dance
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Get in and out of a truck

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to keep or regain your body balance or stay upright when in an unstable position.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Walk on narrow beams in high-rise construction
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Stand on a ladder

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to exert muscle force repeatedly or continuously over time. This involves muscular endurance and resistance to muscle fatigue.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Perform a gymnastics routine using the rings
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Use pruning shears to trim a bush

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to use short bursts of muscle force to propel oneself (as in jumping or sprinting), or to throw an object.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Throw a shot-put in a track meet
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Hit a nail with a hammer

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to exert maximum muscle force to lift, push, pull, or carry objects.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Lift 75-pound bags of cement onto a truck
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Push an empty shopping cart

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to use your abdominal and lower back muscles to support part of the body repeatedly or continuously over time without 'giving out' or fatiguing.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Do 100 sit-ups
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Sit up in an office chair

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators

behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Drill a tooth
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Adjust a room light with a dimmer switch

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators

behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Play the drum set in a jazz band
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Row a boat

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators

behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Shoot a duck in flight
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Ride a bicycle alongside a jogger

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators

behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: When a doorbell and phone ring at the same time, quickly select which to answer first

behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Cut facets in a diamond
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Light a candle

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators

behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Put together the inner workings of a small wrist watch
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Put coins in a parking meter

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to quickly move your hand, your hand together with your arm, or your two hands to grasp, manipulate, or assemble objects.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Perform open heart surgery with surgical instruments
behaviors_abilities.min_anchor_descr: Screw a light bulb into a light socket

behaviors_abilities.title: Fitness and Wellness Coordinators
behaviors_abilities.descr: The ability to quickly respond (with the hand, finger, or foot) to a signal (sound, light, picture) when it appears.
behaviors_abilities.max_anchor_descr: Hit the brake when a pedestrian steps in front of your car
